  # single tumor calling pipeline to process this data.

  # The volume in microliters (ml) of the aliquot(s) derived from the analyte(s) shipped for sequencing and characterization.

  # for variant calling purposes. The GDC may elect to use a single tumor calling
  # pipeline to process this data.
  #

  # Text term that represents the kind of molecular specimen analyte.
  #

  # calling. Only one normal per experimental strategy per case can be selected.
  #

  # pipeline to process this data.

  # for variant calling. Only one normal per experimental strategy per case can be selected.
  #

  # The quantity in micrograms (ug) of the aliquot(s) derived from the analyte(s) shipped for sequencing and characterization.
  #
  aliquot_quantity: Float

  # Weight in grams or volume in mL.
  #

  # Denotes which low-pass WGS normal aliquot the submitter prefers to use for
  # variant calling. Only one normal per experimental strategy per case can be selected.
  #

  # Denotes which WXS normal aliquot the submitter prefers to use for variant
  # calling. Only one normal per experimental strategy per case can be selected.
